headline: GILT Q3 Earnings Top on 58% Y/Y Sales Growth, View Raised, Stock Up 7%
summary: Gilat's Q3 2025 results beat estimates on soaring revenue and strong project wins. A raised 2025 outlook signals continued growth momentum.
